OL,5, An estimated 1.5 million households    
OL,6, across the UK will struggle to pay food
OL,7, and energy bills over the next year, as
OL,8, rising prices and higher taxes squeeze 
OL,9, budgets, according to new research.    
OL,11,FThe National Institute of Economic and 
OL,12,FSocial Research (NIESR) predicted the  
OL,13,FUK will fall into recession this year. 
OL,15,FIt called on Chancellor Rishi Sunak to 
OL,16,Fdo more to stop people sliding into    
OL,17,Fdebt and destitution.                  
OL,19,FThe Treasury said it is providing      
OL,20,Fsupport to households.                 
